GPL-2.0 NOTICE -- BC-250 amdgpu liberation patch series
========================================================

The patch files in this directory (`bc250-cachyos-7.0.9/*.patch`) are diffs
against the Linux kernel (the amdgpu driver / AMD SMU code), applied on top of
a CachyOS 7.0.2 tree. Because they are derivative works of the Linux kernel,
they are licensed **GPL-2.0-only**, the same license as the code they modify --
and the same license (GPL-2.0-only) that covers the arieltune project at the
repository top level.

- Base work: the Linux kernel (https://kernel.org), GPL-2.0-only, (c) its many
  contributors; the CachyOS patch set (https://github.com/CachyOS).
- These patches: (c) 2026 Cachenetics, GPL-2.0-only.

The arieltune top level carries these patches as build assets (applied by the
APU tab's kernel-build path). If you redistribute the patches or a kernel built
from them, they remain GPL-2.0-only.
